<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Credentials — Station8</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/design.css">
</head>
<body>
{{> _nav }}

<div class="swe-container" style="padding-top: var(--space-xxl); padding-bottom: var(--space-section);">

    <div class="swe-flex-between swe-mb-xl">
        <div>
            <h1 class="swe-display-lg" style="margin: 0;">Credentials</h1>
            <p class="swe-body-md swe-mute" style="margin: var(--space-sm) 0 0;">
                Credential vault (M17) — AES-GCM 암호화. value는 등록 후 절대 화면/응답에 노출되지 않음.
                Builder 노드의 credentialId picker에서 type별로 사용 가능.
            </p>
        </div>
        <a href="/admin/credentials/new" class="swe-btn-primary">+ New Credential</a>
    </div>

    {{#flashMsg}}
    <div class="swe-card swe-mb-xl" style="padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg); border-left: 4px solid {{#flashOk}}var(--accent-green){{/flashOk}}{{^flashOk}}var(--accent-pink){{/flashOk}};">
        <code style="color: var(--ink); font-size: 0.95em;">{{flashMsg}}</code>
    </div>
    {{/flashMsg}}

    <div class="swe-grid swe-grid-3 swe-mb-xl">
        <div class="swe-stat-card">
            <div class="swe-stat-label">Total</div>
            <div class="swe-stat-value">{{totalCount}}</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="swe-card" style="padding: 0;">
        <table class="swe-table">
            <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Name</th>
                <th>Type</th>
                <th>Schema</th>
                <th>Created</th>
                <th class="swe-text-right">Actions</th>
            </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
            {{#credentials}}
            <tr>
                <td><strong>{{name}}</strong></td>
                <td><span class="swe-keycap">{{type}}</span></td>
                <td class="swe-mute" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.85em;">
                    {{#schemaJson}}{{schemaJson}}{{/schemaJson}}
                    {{^schemaJson}}—{{/schemaJson}}
                </td>
                <td class="swe-mute">{{regDt}}{{#regId}} · {{regId}}{{/regId}}</td>
                <td class="swe-actions">
                    <a href="/admin/credentials/{{id}}/edit" class="swe-btn-tertiary swe-btn-sm">Edit</a>
                    <form action="/admin/credentials/{{id}}/delete" method="post" style="display:inline;"
                          onsubmit="return confirm('Delete credential &quot;{{name}}&quot;? (soft delete)');">
                        {{> _csrf}}
                        <button type="submit" class="swe-btn-tertiary swe-btn-sm swe-btn-danger">Delete</button>
                    </form>
                </td>
            </tr>
            {{/credentials}}
            {{^credentials}}
            <tr>
                <td colspan="5" class="swe-mute" style="text-align:center; padding: var(--space-xl);">
                    등록된 credential이 없습니다. "+ New Credential"로 추가하세요.
                </td>
            </tr>
            {{/credentials}}
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div class="swe-card swe-mt-xl" style="padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);">
        <h3 class="swe-body-md" style="margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm); color: var(--accent-green);">참고</h3>
        <ul class="swe-mute" style="margin: 0; padding-left: var(--space-lg); font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.7;">
            <li><strong>http_basic</strong>: schema.username + value=password</li>
            <li><strong>http_bearer</strong> / <strong>webhook_hmac</strong> / <strong>generic</strong>: value만</li>
            <li><strong>api_key</strong>: schema.header + value=key (예: <code>X-API-Key</code>)</li>
            <li><strong>openai_compatible</strong>: schema.baseUrl + value=apiKey (로컬 Ollama는 apiKey 빈 값 허용)</li>
            <li><strong>anthropic</strong>: schema.baseUrl(선택, 기본 <code>https://api.anthropic.com</code>) + value=apiKey</li>
            <li><strong>s3_access_key</strong> / <strong>sftp_password</strong> / <strong>sftp_key</strong>: M19 파일 backend용</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
